name: customerInformation
description: Bot for sending user to different tools related with customer information
helpTitle: SAP CAI Intent Bot: Customer Information
helpDescription: This skill can help you to get customer information like their landscape, their projects, their Early Watch Alerts, etc. The bot can also help you by navigating to the existing tools when you need more details.

name: swbControlledIntents
description: Bot to detect intents that are connected with ML models (find Assets and find links)
helpTitle: SAP CAI Intent Bot: Find services, assets, link and other tasks
helpDescription: This skill can provide you with the available services for certain topics or that can support your customer. Besides it can also provide useful links related with the topic that you mention.
